<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.209934>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11. Phlugiolopsis adentis sp. nov. A – F. male: A. pronotum in dorsal view; B. apex of abdomen in dorsal view; C. right cercus in dorsal view; D. right cercus in ventral view, E. ventral process of right cercus in externo-dorsal view, F. subgenital plate in ventral view; G – I. female: G. apex of abdomen in lateral view; H. apex of ovipositor in lateral view; I. subgenital plate in ventral view; d. dorsal valva; v. ventral valva." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/209934/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.209936>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Habitus lateral view of Phlugiolopsis spp. A, C, E, G, I. male; B, D, F, H, J. female: A – B. P. digitusis sp. nov.; C – D. P. tribranchis sp. nov.; E – F. P. adentis sp. nov.; G – H. P. pectinis sp. nov.; I – J. P. trullis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/209936/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

